    "Our 2024 survey invited 115,000 workers across 11 occupations.",
    "Ideally, we would sample an equal number from each-i.e., 10,450 journalists, 10,450 software developers, etc.",
    "However, some occupations in Denmark employ fewer than 10,450 workers.",
    "To address this, we follow these steps:",
    "If an occupation has fewer than 10,450 workers, we sample all available workers."
